metadata.name: Demon Girl #1
metadata.description:
Demon Slayer

Born of a hybrid of oni and human, she possesses strong physical abilities and wisdom.
She has been cared for by humans since she was a baby, so she joins the hunt for oni that stalk humans. She is looking for clues to find out whether her parents are alive or dead.
Features: She likes mochi.

Demon girl#1 stamp will be airdroped to thank all bidders.
